CASE WHEN COALESCE(TFR_EFFECTIVE_DATE,'') <> '' AND TFR_EFFECTIVE_DATE <> '20691231' 
THEN to_date(TRIM(TFR_EFFECTIVE_DATE), 'yyyy-MM-dd') 
WHEN TFR_EFFECTIVE_DATE = '20691231' THEN to_date('9999-12-31','yyyy-MM-dd') 
ELSE to_date('1000-01-03','yyyy-MM-dd') END
